	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am just learning to quadkite, any info/tips&nbsp;&nbsp;you have would be useful.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
